<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3538] Column families allow to have slashes in name</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3538</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The check in HColumnDescriptor.isLegalFamilyName() does not check for slashes and may cause issue.&lt;/p&gt;

